December 23, 2019 |website=Tubular Insights |access-date=December 23, 2019}}</ref> Across Instagram and Twitter over 556,000 posts have garnered more than 4.6 billion views.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.tintup.com/blog/20m-trees-achieved-go-teamtrees/ |title=20M Trees Achieved! Go #TeamTrees |date=December 19, 2019 |website=TINTup.com |language=en-US |access-date=December 20, 2019}}</ref> Creators were able to uniquely inspire their audience to become donors and supporters of Team Trees through their relationships with their fans.<ref name=\"Tubular Insights\" />\n\nIn addition to [[social media]] [[Internet celebrity|influencers]], large corporations made large donations including [[Verizon]],<ref name=\"businsider\" /><ref name=\"verizongreenteam\">{{Cite tweet |number=1189925109194211329 |user=VerizonGreen |title=\ud83c\udf33Tree-rific!\ud83c\udf33We are excited to support #TeamTrees with a contribution of 100,000 trees toward the 20 million tree goal. Our contribution represents 3 trees for every #Verizon Green Team member in 50 countries around the world. #WorkGreenLiveGreen @arborday @MrBeastYT @MarkRober |date=October 31, 2019 |access-date=November 19, 2019}}</ref> [[Electronic Arts|EA]],<ref name=\"plantsvszombiestweet\">{{Cite tweet |number=1201622068460236800 |user=PlantsvsZombies |title=Because more trees = less zombies   In the spirit of Feastivus, we're planting 500,000 trees with @teamtreesofficl |author-link=Plants vs. Zombies |date=December 2, 2019 |access-date=December 3, 2019}}</ref><ref name=\"mrbeastplantsvszombies\">{{Cite tweet |number=1201899624283414528 |user=MrBeastYT |title=Plant Vs Zombies planted 500,000 trees!!!! :))))))))))) |author-link=MrBeast |date=December 3, 2019 |access-date=December 3, 2019}}</ref> [[Salesforce]] ([[Marc Benioff]]), [[Shopify]] (CEO [[Tobias Lutke]]<ref name=\"businsider\" /><ref name=\"futurism\" /><ref name=\"heavy\" /> and CTO [[Jean-Michel Lemieux]]<ref name=businsider/><ref name=marcbeniofftweet/>) and [[